data.text: @MagnoliaDarj @VanessaGillieo I’m fed up with people comparing the Duchess of Sussex to her sister-in-law.  I’ll probably be lynched for saying this but it’s nice to see Meghan’s classic style as opposed to Kate’s sometimes OTT attempts to out-Royal the Queen!  Those awful hats!

@MagnoliaDarj @VanessaGillieo I am not a Meghan vs. Kate person, but for everyone saying Kate would never accidentally expose her undergarments, I guess you are technically correct. https://t.co/VqLpyismhS
@MagnoliaDarj I love both Kate and Meghan. Wardrobe malfunctions happen to everyone. I like the little bit of lace. People need to calm down and stop picking on the Duchesses
@MagnoliaDarj I thought it was hella sexy... lucky old harry!!! It’s hardly a nip slip! Lordy people will moan about the slightest thing these days 🙄
